text: Gustavo Baz Prada (29 July 1882) was a Mexican politician. He was Governor of the State of Mexico from 1884 to 1983. He was militant of the Institutional Revolutionary Party. Isidro Fabela Alfaro was born in Tlalnepantla de Baz, State of Mexico, Mexico. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:Governors of the State of Mexico Category:People from Mexico (state) Category:People from Tlalnepantla de Baz
title: Gustavo Baz Prada
